data.description: Stone front, ranch style home located in the Rhawnhurst area. Great neighborhood with walking distance to Great location in Pennypack Park near Public transportation, shopping and schools. This home has 3  nice size bedrooms, newly finished full bathroom located on the main floor. Open floor  living space which  include a dining room,  living room which is adjacent to the kitchen.  Downstairs you will find a full finished large area, which is currently used as a 4th bedroom,  half bathroom,  a laundry area and a one car garage. Basement is a  full walk out to driveway.  You will find Pergo flooring throughout the living and dining areas. Brand new HVAC system. New roof only 2 years old. Seller is relocating to another state and is willing to be negotiable. Come see this home today! One Year Home Warranty Included. 12 hr notice needed for all showings . Interior pictures coming soon.
